text: Choi Mi-seon (born 30 March 1980) is a South Korean gymnast. She competed in five events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of South Korea Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:People from Yongin
